p: Peter Nelson, W Smith H Elsner C Whaley G Matson Charles Lundblad Dennis Coffrey & Jasob Annir being duly sworn each for himself say that they are the petitioners named in the foregoing petition, that they have heard read the said petition, and know the contents therof, and that the said is the assording to the best of their knowledge and belief
Peter Nelson W Smith H Elsner C Whaley G. Mattson Chalrs Lundblad Dennis his X mark Coffrey Jasob Anner
Subscribed and Sworn to before me this 1st day of May A.D. 1875
